data.description: Beautiful home in KELLER ISD!  Well Maintain in highly desired Heritage Trace, Alliance Corridor. 4 beds, 2 full baths and office space, With and open floor plan, fans with remotes, lawn sprinkler systems, and gutters. Lovely fireplace in main living area, open to large kitchen with island, a lots of cabinet space. Large master suite with dual sinks, garden tub, and walk-in closet. Near to shopping areas and Downtown. easy access to DFW air port and mayor freeways. This beauty is ready and perfect for entertaining! Please come show this house!
